ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectFerry-Boats Remission Order, 2016
PrecisFERRY-BOATS REMISSION ORDER, 2016, waiving the tariff, which is expected to result in savings that will allow ferry operators to reinvest in their fleet renewal plans, enhance ferry services and/or lower their fares for passengers and commercial users.
